te realistic Keychain Logos images ','Create a photorealistic square image (1080x1080) showing a custom acrylic keychain version of the [LOGO] logo hanging from the zipper of a dark-colored backpack (e.g. black or grey). The logo must retain its original shape, color, and proportions without any alteration. The keychain should have a clear glossy acrylic layer, clipped with a silver metal ring and clasp. Use soft daylight or diffused lighting to avoid yellow tones. Set the background in a modern outdoor setting, but keep it blurred to maintain focus on the logo keychain.','/static/uploads/prompts/f98e51be-d752-49e3-bc94-04b9dcc9e399.jpg','2025-09-29 03:13:09',2,3),(216,'LEGO Animals by Nano Banana','Create LEGO Animals by Nano Banana','A hyper-detailed 3D render of a [ANIMAL] made entirely from LEGO bricks. The build should look like an official LEGO set, with clearly visible studs, smooth interlocking parts, and glossy plastic reflections. The [ANIMAL] should be well-proportioned and recognizable, but still obviously constructed from LEGO pieces. Bright studio lighting, clean white background, realistic shadows.\r\n\r\n1080x1080.','/static/uploads/prompts/e6d2e724-4b54-43a1-a04c-68fda3dedcb9.jpg','2025-09-29 03:24:00',2,3),(217,'Chibi Characters','Create Chibi Characters','Hyper-realistic 3D render of a chibi-style\r\n\r\n[CHARACTER] figure, oversized head with authentic [FACIAL/HAIR DETAILS], and cute compact body with large head-to-body ratio. Character is wearing their [ICONIC OUTFIT] and posed dynamically on a sleek metallic platform. Background: futuristic high-tech laboratory or stage with soft blue lighting and blurred bokeh glow. Cinematic LED lighting, photorealistic textures, Pixar-quality collectible figure aesthetic. Slightly low camera angle to emphasize presence despite cute proportions. 1080x1080 square format.','/static/uploads/prompts/7752e466-36f6-4be3-9061-5cc7cbec0d6e.jpg','2025-09-29 03:25:19',2,1),(218,'Modern Samurai','Create realistic Modern Samurai using own face images ','Make the man in the photo a modern samurai warrior standing in a heroic pose in the battle field, with cuts and bruises on his face and body. He is standing strong. Cinematic visual photography.','/static/uploads/prompts/ea5ab8c0-8a67-4e3d-87bd-579cf0ee4370.jpg','2025-09-29 03:26:44',2,2),(219,'3d modeling','create your own images 3d modeling','Create a 1/7 scale commercialized figurine of the characters in the picture, in a realistic style, in a real environment. The figurine is placed on a computer desk. The figurine has a round transparent acrylic base, with no text on the base. The content on the computer screen is a 3D modeling process of this figurine. Next to the computer screen is a toy packaging box, designed in a style reminiscent of high-quality collectible figures, printed with original artwork. The packaging features two-dimensional flat illustrations.','/static/uploads/prompts/9d7d98f4-e7e5-4320-a12b-bee9af61cb3c.jpg','2025-09-29 03:28:59',2,1);
